### images upload
POST http://localhost:{{$dotenv PORT}}/images/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv ACCESS_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary1

--boundary1
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="images"; filename="kackar-mountains-9655201_1920.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./images/kackar-mountains-9655201_1920.jpg

--boundary1
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="images"; filename="rock-formation-7404192_1920.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./images/rock-formation-7404192_1920.jpg
--boundary1--

### image upload
POST http://localhost:{{$dotenv PORT}}/image/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv ACCESS_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary1

--boundary1
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="read-9370928_1920.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./images/read-9370928_1920.jpg
--boundary1--

### image get
@path = 
GET http://localhost:{{$dotenv PORT}}/image/{{path}}

DELETE http://localhost:{{$dotenv PORT}}/image/{{path}}
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv ACCESS_TOKEN}}